snippet.textDisplay: Not sure how I feel about this- it took me about three minutes to realise this was Dama Dam Mast. It sounds so different, and in this case, I'm not personally a fan. I'd have liked it if they stuck more closely to the sound and feel of the original, but I respect their effort to change it and spice it up, just didn't fully work for me. I read somewhere that Umair Jaswal was meant to sing this- with his voice, and something closer to the original composition, it would have been a mega-hit
